OL,3,COfgem to confirm latest energy price
OL,4,Ccap for household bills
OL,6,FOfgem is expected to confirm that
OL,7,Fhousehold energy bills will fall by
OL,8,Faround 7% from July when it updates
OL,9,Fits latest price cap on Friday.
OL,11,FThe typical bill is expected to fall
OL,12,Fby #129 to #1,720 per year when the
OL,13,Fregulator's new price cap ` which sets
OL,14,Fthe limit on how much firms can charge
OL,15,Fcustomers per unit of energy ` comes
OL,16,Finto force, experts at Cornwall
OL,17,FInsight have predicted.
