OL,3,COfgem to confirm latest energy price
OL,4,Ccap for household bills
OL,6,FThe price cap is currently set at
OL,7,Faround #1,849 for a typical household
OL,8,Fafter three consecutive increases in
OL,9,Fbills.
OL,11,FIt is set to fall after US President
OL,12,FDonald Trump's aggressive tariff plans
OL,13,Fled to a significant slump in gas and
OL,14,Foil prices.
OL,16,FHowever, the predicted drop is
OL,17,Fslightly less than the previously
OL,18,Fforecast 9% fall following an easing
OL,19,Fof trade tensions in recent weeks.
