OL,3,COfgem to confirm latest energy price
OL,4,Ccap for household bills
OL,6,FCornwall Insight said it expects the
OL,7,Freduced price cap to be followed by a
OL,8,F"modest drop" in October and another
OL,9,Fsimilar dip in January next year.
OL,11,FNews of a fall in energy costs will
OL,12,Fcome as a relief for households, who
OL,13,Fsuffered through an "awful April" of
OL,14,Fbill rises, including Ofgem's last
OL,15,F6.4% price cap increase.
