OL,3,COfgem to confirm latest energy price
OL,4,Ccap for household bills
OL,6,FUnder-pressure households have also
OL,7,Fbeen hit with the biggest increase to
OL,8,Fwater bills since at least February
OL,9,F1988, alongside steep increases across
OL,10,Fbills for council tax, mobile and
OL,11,Fbroadband tariffs, as well as road tax.
OL,13,FBill rises have led to Consumer Prices
OL,14,FIndex (CPI) inflation jumping to 3.5%
OL,15,Fin April, up from 2.6% in March and
OL,16,Fthe highest since January 2024.
