OL,3,COfgem to confirm latest energy price
OL,4,Ccap for household bills
OL,6,FOn Monday, Craig Lowrey, principal
OL,7,Fconsultant at Cornwall Insight, said:
OL,8,F"The fall in the price cap is a
OL,9,Fwelcome development and will bring
OL,10,Fmuch-needed breathing space for
OL,11,Fhouseholds after a prolonged period of
OL,12,Fhigh energy costs.
OL,14,F"It's a step in the right direction,
OL,15,Fbut it should be taken in context.
