OL,3,COfgem to confirm latest energy price
OL,4,Ccap for household bills
OL,6,F"Prices are falling, but not by enough
OL,7,Ffor the numerous households struggling
OL,8,Funder the weight of a cost-of-living
OL,9,Fcrisis, and bills remain well above
OL,10,Fthe levels seen at the start of the
OL,11,Fdecade.
OL,13,F"As such, there remains a risk that
OL,14,Fenergy will remain unaffordable for
OL,15,Fmany."
OL,17,FOfgem changes the price cap for
OL,18,Fhouseholds every three months, largely
OL,19,Fbased on the cost of energy on
OL,20,Fwholesale markets.
